{"text": " This audio offers some simple practical guidance for preparing your meditation space. Creating supportive conditions can help the mind settle more easily and encourage a steady, grounded meditation practice. Choose a quiet place with as few distractions as possible. Keep the space simple and uncluttered, allowing only what is necessary to remain. If you can, use soft or dimmed lighting to create a gentle atmosphere. These are simply recommendations. We understand that ideal conditions are not always available. Practice with what you have, the most important thing is to meditate. Every moment of practice is", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 5.460000000000002, "end": 13.12, "text": " This audio offers some simple practical guidance for preparing your meditation space.", "tokens": [50364, 639, 6278, 7736, 512, 2199, 8496, 10056, 337, 10075, 428, 12537, 1901, 13, 51410], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.25103479273178997, "compression_ratio": 1.3511450381679388, "no_speech_prob": 0.0661543682217598, "words": [{"word": " This", "start": 5.460000000000002, "end": 6.58, "probability": 0.8140419721603394}, {"word": " audio", "start": 6.58, "end": 7.12, "probability": 0.9694803357124329}, {"word": " offers", "start": 7.12, "end": 7.68, "probability": 0.9914912581443787}, {"word": " some", "start": 7.68, "end": 8.0, "probability": 0.9765288233757019}, {"word": " simple", "start": 8.0, "end": 8.52, "probability": 0.9954736828804016}, {"word": " practical", "start": 8.52, "end": 9.54, "probability": 0.5724611282348633}, {"word": " guidance", "start": 9.54, "end": 10.06, "probability": 0.9976935982704163}, {"word": " for", "start": 10.06, "end": 10.58, "probability": 0.9866037368774414}, {"word": " preparing", "start": 10.58, "end": 11.2, "probability": 0.9956737160682678}, {"word": " your", "start": 11.2, "end": 11.62, "probability": 0.9941790103912354}, {"word": " meditation", "start": 11.62, "end": 12.14, "probability": 0.9736234545707703}, {"word":